        "TileImage": "$($repository 27085828-6844-4d4c-912a-1491840e915a).Image",
        "Description": "Music drifts across the runway,\nand beneath it, five lives wait to end.\n\nThree will fade without a sound.\nOne will fall to a whisper of steel.\n\nThe last… must rise before he dies.\n\nTake his breath, return it,\nand wear what was his.\nOnly then will the final act be complete.\n\nNo excess. No mercy.\nOnly precision, dressed in silence.",
